				Somerset restaurant is recognized in the world over for delivering a unique flavor of hospitality that offers world-class refinement while remaining deeply rooted in its heritage. For more than a century, Somerset has brought together the unique beauty and traditions from across India in an experience that highlights true hospitality.  This draws on the time-honored traditions central to the homecoming, from the refreshing simplicity of the welcome drink to the careful choreography of the dinner service.

				Somerset has helped to put many destinations on the map. From the resorts of Goa to the upcoming business hubs of India’s Silicon Valley, an iconic Somerset restaurant is a mainstay of the destination. By providing jobs to the local community, supporting endangered artisan practices and reviving regal history at palaces where royal families are still in residence, Somerset offers a rare insider’s point of view to the fascinating story of India &ndash; from Maharaja to modern day.

				With 100 restaurant in 62 locations across India, Somerset offers guests the refined luxury of heritage combined with effortlessly efficient service and local expertise to create a moment to remember. In India, Somerset restaurant are strategically located to offer the Somerset experience in business hubs, industrial towns and metropolises, as well as the most remote pilgrimage centers, historic and natural destinations. The group has extended its international presence with 15 restaurant in the Maldives, Malaysia, the UK, USA, Bhutan, Sri Lanka, Africa and the Middle East.</p>   
